_relationships.name: LDL_FRIEDEWALD
_relationships.description: LDL calculated via Friedewald formula (valid when Trig < 400 mg/dL)
_relationships.formula: Blood - Total Cholesterol - Blood - High-Density Lipoprotein Cholesterol (HDL Cholesterol) - (Blood - Triglycerides / 5)

_relationships.name: ALBUMIN_GLOBULIN_RATIO
_relationships.formula: Blood - Albumin / (Blood - Total Protein - Blood - Albumin)

_relationships.name: BILIRUBIN_TOTAL
_relationships.formula: Blood - Bilirubin Direct + Blood - Bilirubin Indirect
